thread.title: Students protest as White House grapples with background checks

title: Students protest as White House grapples with background checks
text:
Students protest as White House grapples with background checks 5:32am EST - 02:02 
Protests against gun violence in schools are taking off after a high school shooting in Florida left 17 dead. The White House said on Monday it backs efforts to improve background checks on gun purchases. Colette Luke has more.
